# <a name="saving-messages-in-outlookcom"></a><span data-ttu-id="8d7ea-102">Spara meddelanden i Outlook.com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8d7ea-102">Saving messages in Outlook.com</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8d7ea-103">Du kan inte spara e-postmeddelanden i Outlook.com, men du kan skriva ut dem till en PDF-fil som du kan spara på din PC.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8d7ea-103">You cannot save email messages in Outlook.com, but you can print them to a PDF which you can save on your PC.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8d7ea-104">Med Microsoft Skriv ut till PDF-verktyget i Windows 10 kan du skriva ut ett e-postmeddelande direkt till en PDF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8d7ea-104">The Microsoft Print To PDF utility included in Windows 10 allows you to print any email message directly to a PDF.</span></span>

1. <span data-ttu-id="8d7ea-105">Markera det meddelande som du vill spara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8d7ea-105">Select the message you want to save.</span></span>
2. <span data-ttu-id="8d7ea-106">Markera de tre punkterna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8d7ea-106">Select the three dots</span></span> <img src='data:image/png;base64,' />
 <span data-ttu-id="8d7ea-107">högst upp i meddelandet och välj sedan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8d7ea-107">at the top of the message and then select</span></span> <img src='data:image/png;base64,' />
 <span data-ttu-id="8d7ea-108">**Skriv ut**.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8d7ea-108">**Print**.</span></span>
3. <span data-ttu-id="8d7ea-109">Välj **Skriv ut** igen och välj **Microsoft Skriv ut till PDF**i den nedrullningsbara menyn skrivare.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8d7ea-109">Select **Print** again, and from the printer drop-down menu, select **Microsoft Print to PDF**.</span></span>
4. <span data-ttu-id="8d7ea-110">Välj **Skriv ut**.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8d7ea-110">Select **Print**.</span></span>
5. <span data-ttu-id="8d7ea-111">Ange ett fil namn och välj sedan **Spara**.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8d7ea-111">Enter a file name then select **Save**.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8d7ea-112">**Obs!** Detta rekommenderas inte på delade eller offentliga datorer eftersom andra användare kan ha till gång till alla PDF-filer som du sparar på datorn och inte ta bort.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8d7ea-112">**Note:** This is not recommended on shared or public computers as other users could have access to any PDFs you save to the PC and don't delete.</span></span>
